OL,3,CPlans to demolish eight tower blocks
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FBrighton and Hove City Council has
OL,7,Fconfirmed it will push ahead with
OL,8,Fplans to demolish eight tower blocks
OL,9,Facross three locations in the city,
OL,10,Famid safety concerns.
OL,12,FThe buildings, containing 554 flats,
OL,13,Fno longer meet modern safety
OL,14,Fstandards, and a recent report
OL,15,Frecommended they be pulled down and
OL,16,Freplaced with new council homes.
