OL,6,FThe buildings are Dudeney Lodge and
OL,7,FNettleton Court in Hollingdean, Falcon
OL,8,FCourt, Heron Court, Kestrel Court,
OL,9,FKingfisher Court and Swallow Court in
OL,10,Fnorth Whitehawk and St James's House
OL,11,Fin Kemp Town.
OL,13,FThe council says structural surveys
OL,14,Flast year found the buildings no
OL,15,Flonger meet current safety standards
OL,16,Ffor withstanding a collapse in the
OL,17,Fcase of an explosion or large fire.
