OL,3,CPlans to demolish eight tower blocks
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FThe council looked at strengthening
OL,7,Fand refurbishing the buildings but
OL,8,Fresearch found these methods would
OL,9,Fonly guarantee their safety for 20
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FCouncillor Gill Williams, Cabinet
OL,13,FMember for Housing, said: "This is a
OL,14,Fbig step, but after very careful
OL,15,Fconsideration of the options, we have
OL,16,Fagreed in principle that regeneration
OL,17,Fis the preferred option.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
