OL,6,F"Since October last year, I have been
OL,7,Fworking with officers and meeting with
OL,8,Fhouseholders to explore the options
OL,9,Fabout the future of these blocks.
OL,11,F"We recognise that these buildings
OL,12,Fhave happy memories, in some cases for
OL,13,F3 generations of families.
OL,15,F"This is why it was important for us
OL,16,Fto explore all the options in detail,
OL,17,Fincluding strengthening and
OL,18,Frefurbishing the blocks. That would
OL,19,Fonly buy us 20 more years, at great
OL,20,Fcost and disruption, without solving
OL,21,Fthe core safety issues.
