OL,6,F"By creating more family sized homes
OL,7,Fin the city, it should reduce wait for
OL,8,Fa 3-bedroom home down from the average
OL,9,Fof 8 years.
OL,11,F"We will now begin working hand-in-
OL,12,Fhand with residents on every step of
OL,13,Fthe next part of the journey.
OL,15,F"We're holding the first Resident
OL,16,FAdvisory Panels for each area in the
OL,17,Fcoming weeks. These have been set up
OL,18,Fto ensure any regeneration designs
OL,19,Freflect the needs, the voices and the
OL,20,Fvision of residents.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
