OL,6,F"Our other key focus is to set up
OL,7,Frehousing teams to start supporting
OL,8,Fresidents to plan their moves. This is
OL,9,Fa big task and will be done in phases
OL,10,Fover a number of years. We're
OL,11,Freassuring residents that no-one will
OL,12,Fhave to move immediately.
OL,14,F"We will support every resident
OL,15,Fthrough the rehousing process, and we
OL,16,Fwill do everything we can to help them
OL,17,Fstay in your local community if that's
OL,18,Fwhat they want."
